":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔用&ldquo;放&rdquo;字咁應該用咩字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n播？</blockquote><br />\n自己識發光嘅熒幕(如電視機、電腦mon)先會用&ldquo;播&rdquo;字<br />\n戲院係用銀幕，自己唔識發光，要用放映機投射落銀幕，所以用&ldquo;放&rdquo;字係最合適，唔知d人屌乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你作架？</blockquote><br />\n應該用播字囉  廣東話用放 都唔通順</blockquote><br />\n戲院喎, 以我理解, 投射機器用放/放映<br />\n經大氣電波用播/播映<br />\n即係同樓上意思差唔多"},{"pid":"5ec9c153166bc45526e261bf7788f96e2f4b5e3c","tid":118602,"uid":33190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔用&ldquo;放&rdquo;字咁應該用咩字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n播？</blockquote><br />\n自己識發光嘅熒幕(如電視機、電腦mon)先會用&ldquo;播&rdquo;字<br />\n戲院係用銀幕，自己唔識發光，要用放映機投射落銀幕，所以用&ldquo;放&rdquo;字係最合適，唔知d人屌乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你作架？</blockquote><br />\n應該用播字囉  廣東話用放 都唔通順</blockquote><br />\n戲院喎, 以我理解, 投射機器用放/放映<br />\n經大氣電波用播/播映<br />\n即係同樓上意思差唔多</blockquote><br />\n我覺得樓上講有道理<br />\n連登點解小學雞多，啲人自己字都唔睇過幾多粒，學人扮專家，懶係話人錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大把語法，別寫，用詞你地未見過，下下以為得自己果套最正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13679aec4868b279043b8070dc68e8b3b6a68abb","tid":118602,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:00:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾到不得了嘅女性ff戲，水平接近大陸宮庭爭寵小說"},{"pid":"20b898a0a6020124859232c13f20ad0d9c4d7de6","tid":118602,"uid":48479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔用&ldquo;放&rdquo;字咁應該用咩字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n播？</blockquote><br />\n自己識發光嘅熒幕(如電視機、電腦mon)先會用&ldquo;播&rdquo;字<br />\n戲院係用銀幕，自己唔識發光，要用放映機投射落銀幕，所以用&ldquo;放&rdquo;字係最合適，唔知d人屌乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你作架？</blockquote><br />\n應該用播字囉  廣東話用放 都唔通順</blockquote><br />\n無論你查任何字典，&quot;Screening&quot;都係會譯做&ldquo;放映&rdquo;，唔會係&ldquo;播映&rdquo;，&ldquo;Broadcast&rdquo;先會譯做&ldquo;播映&rdquo;。<br />\n林奕華曾經寫過一本書叫《是銀幕不是熒幕，是放映不是播映：當女明星還是大女明星》。<br />\n如果你堅持要講&ldquo;播(映)&rdquo;，我唔會逼你改口，但我會堅持你係錯。"},{"pid":"965024097a491fe51db259b2f6c7dfccb461c0ff","tid":118602,"uid":39938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"騎劫咗"},{"pid":"4fb9e906f825cdfaf56d5bde213da6029bce2a38","tid":118602,"uid":37300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0aK9x16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0aK9x16.jpg&h=a0added7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"890bffb05bb4aa7558ca75e095c75e38e942170e","tid":118602,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>騎劫咗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵人開過post"},{"pid":"3e651799c29960d4e13d7d2dfa780282a294a03b","tid":118602,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"放同播明顯唔同wor <br />\n<br />\n放：投影機射埋牆睇野<br />\n播：睇緊個部機播d野出黎"}]}